data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 270 Halibut Circle in charming Covington, Georgia. This stunning move-in ready home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. It boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms with generous living spaces, with an open floor plan that is perfect for both daily living and entertaining. With the multiple living areas, there is plenty of room for family or guests to spread out and enjoy. The heart of the home is the beautifully appointed kitchen, complete with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and an expansive island. Whether you're cooking for one or cooking for a crowd, you'll appreciate this well-designed space. For the quieter times you're seeking, retreat to your private oasis in the primary suite, featuring a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and large bathroom with double vanities and a soaking tub. Secondary bedrooms are spacious as well. You can start enjoying your new home from day one without the hassle of renovations or repairs. Conveniently situated minutes away from I-20, near schools, parks, shopping, and dining.  For dog lovers, this community provides a walking trail and several curb station locations.  Yes, the whole house water purification system inside the garage will remain.  After closing you will be able to download the GOOGLE home app and control the lights, lock, camera, and alarm. ***SELLER MAY HELP WITH CLOSING COSTS***
